     fhir:Narrative.status [ fhir:value "extensions" ] ;
     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet RevisionAarsagDKRR</b></p><a name=\"RevisionAarsagDKRR\"> </a><a name=\"hcRevisionAarsagDKRR\"> </a><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionCause.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/RevisionCause</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionCause.html#RevisionCause-trauma\">trauma</a></td><td>Nyt traume</td><td>Trauma / traume</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionCause.html#RevisionCause-tunnelwidening\">tunnelwidening</a></td><td>Tunnelwidening</td><td>Tunnelwidening</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionCause.html#RevisionCause-suboptimal_graft_tibia\">suboptimal_graft_tibia</a></td><td>Suboptimal graft placering i tibia</td><td>Suboptimal graft; placement in tibia / Suboptimal graft placering i tibia</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionCause.html#RevisionCause-suboptimal_graft_femur\">suboptimal_graft_femur</a></td><td>Suboptimal graft placering i femur</td><td>Suboptimal graft; placement in femur / Suboptimal graft placering i femur</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionCause.html#RevisionCause-infection\">infection</a></td><td>Infektion</td><td>Infection / Infektion</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-RevisionCause.html#RevisionCause-ligamental_instability\">ligamental_instability</a></td><td>Anden ligamentær løshed som årsag til ny instabilitet</td><td>Other ligamental looseness causing instability / Anden ligamentær løshed som årsag til ny instabilitet</td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.2.0/CodeSystem-v2-0532.html\"><code>http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v2-0532</code></a><span title=\"Version is explicitly stated to be 3.0.0\"> version ?3.0.0</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"http://terminology.hl7.org/7.2.0/CodeSystem-v2-0532.html#v2-0532-UNK\">UNK</a></td><td>Ukendt årsag til ny instabilitet</td><td>unknown</td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-GenericValues.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/GenericValues</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-GenericValues.html#GenericValues-other\">other</a></td><td>Andet</td><td>Other - used to choose unspecific value not in a valueset</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"
